> <OLD - Hydras>
>
> "You three will come with me" hissed hyddras "i need my most trusted
> warriors with me"
>
> The snake-like heads moved around Hydras's heads as if they whispering
> things to Hydras.

There was a nod from SKYSHADOW as he glanced at VICE GRIP and DINOBOT
and then back at HYDRAS, "Of course sir." His voice once again
sounding like the loyal servant. But as we know, appearances can be
decieving as his watchful optics carefully examining HYDRAS' talking
heads, a calculating glint in his other wise subservient appearing
optics, as his right 'hand' which was more lioke some large claw
'clacked' against each other.

> <OLD>
>
> BLACKARACHNIA continued to walk along, "Well then.  For now, my assets will
> have to remain in..  My possession.  Talk to me if you're ever willing to
> brook a trade to get access to them."
>
> Spider-Sense Tingling!

<NEW>

There was a interested look in his optic as he turned his full gaze on
BLACKARACHNIA, "You present an interesting . . . *ahem* . . .
proposition, but I would think that access to your assets may cost me
more than I would imagine."

Glancing at HYDRAS for a moment and then back at BLACKARACHNIA, "Plus
I would imagine that you would report anything I tell you back to
Tarantulus." His wings flexed smoothly behind him, almost like a robe
or a cloak shifting as he moved.

> <OLD>
>
> BLACKARACHNIA sent her assent along it, for now walking after CRYOTEK to
> follow him along with his orders.

There was a chuckle from TARANTULUS as he muted his side of the
channel. He could still hear, but was not allowing anyting from his
side be transmitted to BLACKARACHNIA.

(TAG)

Preston
